snippet.title: Moonshell Island Teaser - Patron-exclusive demo out now!
snippet.description:
Teaser Demo available now to our Patreon supporters!
https://www.patreon.com/cheekynauts

Moonshell Island is an in-development action RPG featuring an action battle system, story-driven quests, unique mini-games and a tale of achieving dreams as you rescue your growing community from danger.

Release Date: TBD
Platforms: PC

Developed by Cheekynauts Entertainment Ltd.
http://www.cheekynauts.com
https://twitter.com/Cheekynauts

Music by Anna E. (https://annaeichenauer.com) aka @queergermangirl (https://twitter.com/QueerGermanGirl)

Voice-over by Gabriel Castro (https://www.gabrielcastrova.com) aka GabeCastro (https://www.youtube.com/GabeCastroOfficial)
